PLOT
When legions of monstrous creatures, known as Kaiju, started rising from

pilot (Charlie Hunnam) and an untested trainee (Rinko Kikuchi) - who are 
teamed to drive a legendary but seemingly obsolete Jaeger from the past. 
Together, they stand as mankind's last hope against the mounting 
apocalypse.
